	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Generally I prefer 4-op FM chips like YM2612 or YM2151 over wavetable chips like the SPC. But the organ in the SNES version of Dracula X sounds really good, so I'll have to pick that one as my favorite. The PCECD version is also good, but it's basically the SNES version converted to CD-DA.

		

