		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Am I the only one that doesn't like Bloody Tears?
<br />
<br />Of all the songs on the CV2 soundtrack, it's by far the worst one (unless you count the song that plays in Dracula's Castle), yet is the most popular/widespread/covered/remade.
<br />
<br />Same with Vampire Killer.  It's topped by pretty much every other song on the CV1 soundtrack (why oh why doesn't level 5's music get the attention it deserves), yet it's the most popular.
<br />
<br />Anyway I voted for the SNES Dracula X version, but I didn't really listen to the 'others' posted.

		

		</td>
